<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
      body {
          font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
          line-height: 1.6;
          color: #333;
          background-color: #f5f5f5;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
          max-width: 600px;
          margin: 20px auto;
          background-color: #fff;
          border-radius: 8px;
          overflow: hidden;
          box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .header {
          background: <%= @target_type == 'test' ? 'linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%)' : 'linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%)' %>;
          color: white;
          padding: 30px 20px;
          text-align: center;
      }

      .header h1 {
          margin: 0;
          font-size: 24px;
          font-weight: 600;
      }

      .header .badge {
          display: inline-block;
          background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
          padding: 8px 16px;
          border-radius: 20px;
          margin-top: 10px;
          font-size: 14px;
          font-weight: 500;
      }

      .content {
          padding: 30px 20px;
      }

      .greeting {
          font-size: 16px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .alert-box {
          background-color: #fff3cd;
          border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
          padding: 15px;
          margin: 20px 0;
          border-radius: 4px;
      }

      .alert-box strong {
          color: #856404;
      }

      .info-section {
          background-color: #f8f9fa;
          padding: 20px;
          margin: 20px 0;
          border-radius: 4px;
          border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      }

      .info-section h3 {
          margin-top: 0;
          margin-bottom: 15px;
          font-size: 18px;
          color: #495057;
          font-weight: 600;
      }

      .info-item {
          margin: 10px 0;
          display: flex;
          justify-content: space-between;
          padding: 8px 0;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      }

      .info-item:last-child {
          border-bottom: none;
      }

      .info-label {
          font-weight: 600;
          color: #6c757d;
      }

      .info-value {
          color: #212529;
          text-align: right;
      }

      .status-pending {
          display: inline-block;
          background-color: #fff3cd;
          color: #856404;
          padding: 4px 12px;
          border-radius: 12px;
          font-size: 14px;
          font-weight: 600;
      }

      .button {
          display: inline-block;
          padding: 14px 32px;
          background: <%= @target_type == 'test' ? 'linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%)' : 'linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%)' %>;
          color: white !important;
          text-decoration: none;
          border-radius: 6px;
          font-weight: 600;
          font-size: 16px;
          margin: 20px 0;
          text-align: center;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
          transition: transform 0.2s;
      }

      .button:hover {
          transform: translateY(-2px);
          box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      }

      .button-container {
          text-align: center;
          margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .footer {
          background-color: #f8f9fa;
          padding: 20px;
          text-align: center;
          font-size: 12px;
          color: #6c757d;
          border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      }

      .footer a {
          color: #667eea;
          text-decoration: none;
      }

      .highlight {
          background-color: #fff3cd;
          padding: 2px 6px;
          border-radius: 3px;
          font-weight: 600;
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>결제 확인이 필요합니다</h1>
    <div class="badge"><%= @target_type == 'test' ? '시험' : '강의' %></div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="greeting">
      안녕하세요, <strong><%= @user.name %></strong>님!
    </div>

    <div class="alert-box">
      신청하신 <strong><%= @target_name_ko %></strong>가
      <strong style="font-size: 18px; color: #dc3545;"><%= @days_until_start %>일 후</strong>에 시작되는데,
      아직 <strong>결제가 완료되지 않았습니다</strong>.
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
      <h3><%= @target_type == 'test' ? '시험 정보' : '강의 정보' %></h3>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label"><%= @target_type == 'test' ? '시험명' : '강의명' %>:</span>
        <span class="info-value"><strong><%= @target.title %></strong></span>
      </div>
      <% if @target.description.present? %>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">설명:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= truncate(@target.description, length: 50) %></span>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">시작일시:</span>
        <span class="info-value"><%= @target.start_at.strftime('%Y년 %m월 %d일 (%a) %H:%M') %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">종료일시:</span>
        <span class="info-value"><%= @target.end_at.strftime('%Y년 %m월 %d일 (%a) %H:%M') %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">소요시간:</span>
        <span class="info-value">
          <%= distance_of_time_in_words(@target.start_at, @target.end_at) %>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
      <h3>결제 정보</h3>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">결제 금액:</span>
        <span class="info-value">
            <strong style="font-size: 18px; color: #28a745;">
              <%= number_to_currency(@payment.amount, unit: '', precision: 0, delimiter: ',') %>원
            </strong>
          </span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">결제 방법:</span>
        <span class="info-value"><%= @payment.method&.upcase || '미선택' %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">결제 상태:</span>
        <span class="info-value"><span class="status-pending">미완료 (PENDING)</span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">신청일:</span>
        <span class="info-value"><%= @payment.created_at.strftime('%Y년 %m월 %d일 %H:%M') %></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="line-height: 1.8; color: #495057; background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px;">
      <strong style="color: #dc3545;"><%= @target_name_ko %> 시작 전까지</strong> 결제를 완료하지 않으시면
      <span class="highlight"><%= @target_action_ko %>이 불가능</span>할 수 있습니다.<br><br>
      지금 바로 결제를 완료하시고 <%= @target_name_ko %>에 참여하세요!
    </p>

    <div class="button-container">
      <a href="<%= payment_url(@payment) %>" class="button">
        결제 완료하기
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6c757d; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
      결제 ID: <%= @payment.id %><br>
      <%= @target_type == 'test' ? '시험' : '강의' %> ID: <%= @target.id %>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>
      문의사항이 있으시면 <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>으로 연락주세요.<br>
      본 메일은 발신 전용이므로 회신하실 수 없습니다.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 11px;">
      &copy; 2025 My Registration API. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>